OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fcontinuing this evening before easing
OL,7,Fsomewhat overnight, with some clear
OL,8,Fspells developing across the region
OL,9,Fthough the early hours of the morning.
OL,10,FWinds slowly easing too.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FMuch drier on Friday, though
OL,13,Flighter showers possible in places.
OL,14,FVariable amounts of cloud with bright
OL,15,For sunny spells for many. Feeling cool
OL,16,Ffor the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
