OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,6,Fwindy at first on Saturday with rain,
OL,7,Feasing later. Bright spells and
OL,8,Fshowers on Sunday. Overnight rain
OL,9,Fclearing on Monday to sunny spells and
OL,10,Fshowers again. Near normal
OL,11,Ftemperatures.
